# Add and Mount a New Disk in Ubuntu / Kali VM (Persistent Storage)

This guide explains how to add a new hard disk in a virtual machine and configure it so the disk remains mounted after reboot.

Tested on:
- Ubuntu
- Kali Linux
- VMware Workstation

